Class ReusingDBIDFactory

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBIDFactory

    public class ReusingDBIDFactory
extends SimpleDBIDFactory
    Slightly more complex DBID management, that allows reuse of DBIDs. NOT tested a lot yet. Not reusing is much simpler! TODO: manage fragmentation of ranges?
    Since:
    0.4.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
